·金林（Erika Goldring）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Brittany-Howard-and-Zac-Cockrell-of-Alabama-Shakes.-Credit-Erika-Goldring.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Brittany-Howard-and-Zac-Cockrell-of-Alabama-Shakes.-Credit-Erika-Goldring-400x248.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Brittany-Howard-and-Zac-Cockrell-of-Alabama-Shakes.-Credit-Erika-Goldring-800x496.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Brittany-Howard-and-Zac-Cockrell-of-Alabama-Shakes.-Credit-Erika-Goldring-696x432.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Brittany-Howard-and-Zac-Cockrell-of-Alabama-Shakes.-Credit-Erika-Goldring-1392x863.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Brittany-Howard-and-Zac-Cockrell-of-Alabama-Shakes.-Credit-Erika-Goldring-1068x662.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>阿拉巴马州的摇摇在八年来取笑了他们的第一场新音乐，并分享了2025年的节日演出的细节。</p><p>乐队在录音室里的Instagram上发布了一系列图片，乐队写道：“制作一些令人兴奋的东西！”</p><p>鼓手史蒂夫·约翰逊（Steve Johnson）没有出现在图片中。他于2021年3月<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/alabama-shakes-drummer-steven-william-johnson-arrested-on-child-abuse-charges-2909283">因虐待儿童而被捕</a>，但随后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/alabama-shakes-drummer-steve-johnson-has-child-abuse-charges-dismissed-3122428">在2021年12月被解雇</a>。</p><p>这将是他们自“ Killer Diller Blues”以来的第一个新音乐，他们对美国史诗般的音乐会（原始电影配乐）对音乐的贡献。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DFV5iMrJ9E2/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; h