：蒂姆·莫森费尔德（Tim Mosenfelder）和卢克·布伦南（Luke Brennan）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Bowling-For-Soup-and-Wheatus.-Credit-Tim-Mosenfelder-and-Luke-Brennan-via-GETTY.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Bowling-For-Soup-and-Wheatus.-Credit-Tim-Mosenfelder-and-Luke-Brennan-via-GETTY-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Bowling-For-Soup-and-Wheatus.-Credit-Tim-Mosenfelder-and-Luke-Brennan-via-GETTY-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Bowling-For-Soup-and-Wheatus.-Credit-Tim-Mosenfelder-and-Luke-Brennan-via-GETTY-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Bowling-For-Soup-and-Wheatus.-Credit-Tim-Mosenfelder-and-Luke-Brennan-via-GETTY-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Bowling-For-Soup-and-Wheatus.-Credit-Tim-Mosenfelder-and-Luke-Brennan-via-GETTY-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/Bowling-For-Soup">保龄球的汤</a>宣布了今年年底在伦敦的温布利竞技场举行的大规模表演。</p><p>乐队由Jaret Reddick，Gary Wiseman和Rob <a href="/artists/Wheatus">Felicetti</a>组成，将在12月13日的假期期间接管标志性地区。Wheatus和Punk Rock Factory之类的人将作为开放式支持。当地时间上午10点（1月29日），将在周三上午10点出售门票预售，一般门票销售将于周五（1月31日）当地时间上午10点开始。访问<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fbowling-for-soup-tickets%2Fartist%2F835888" target="_blank" rel="noopener">此处</a>购买门票。</p><p>在谈到节目（Per <a href="https://rocksound.tv/news/bowling-for-soup-announce-wembley-arena-show" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Rocksound</em></a> ）时，主唱Jaret Reddick说：“温布利……我能说什么？！？当我们在2000年首次开始打英国时，您永远不会告诉我有一天，我们将成为令人垂涎的温布利竞技场的标题！更多，我们要花30年才能到达那里！！” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DFYWlfyNwqO/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-r